parameters:
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "I still can't get a hold of Cotton's whereabouts...
I asked Teacher Achiri to inquire with her parents, and it
seems they are in contact, but..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Skipping school and slacking off somewhere? If
it's a locker, there are plenty around town, right?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "No, there have been sightings of her commuting to
school. She must be within the academy at least..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: (I can't exactly say that I've set up a hidden camera
in front of the school gate, can I?)
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Then... could it be that blonde phantom...?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "That's likely... Damn it! I'm always one step
behind!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_true]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "By the way, where did that phantom person come
from and where did they go? It seemed like they teleported
naturally, so I didn't really think about it."
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_true]\AA[1]Akane: "!!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_true]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "If you think about it... maybe Cotton is in the
same place they're coming and going from."
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_true]\AA[1]Akane: "What do you mean by that!?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_true]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Like another world? Since they can teleport,
maybe that's possible...?"
\F[beni_smile]Akane: "I see, uh-huh!!"

\F[beni_smile]Akane: "Amazing... I hadn't thought of that. You're
incredible, Nadeshiko!!"
\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Is that so...?"

\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "The reason we can't find her no matter how much we
search the academy is another world... After seeing that
ability, it wouldn't be surprising!"

\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "But... if that's the case, wouldn't it be even
harder to search for her...?"

\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "No, that's okay. If we have a lead, the way we
inquire can change."

\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "We just need to focus more on the mysterious
phenomena occurring at the academy. We might be able to
catch their tail!!"

\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "You seem to have a flash of inspiration. You
look like a detective right now, Akane."
\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Huh?"

\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "You have a good look on your face... You were
irritated just a moment ago, so you're shining even more
now."
\F[beni_shy]\FF[nako_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Is that so...?"

\F[beni_shy]\FF[nako_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: (As usual, Akane seems not used to being
praised.)

\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Then let's go ask Suzukake-senpai and Inukai-sensei
right away. They might know something."
\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Yeah, we need to find Cotton quickly..."
A

\F[beni_angry2]Akane: "That's it... you've taken the bait! Now, let's
settle this!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Amma: "You bastard! That's amazing... you're only helping
out those who aren't part of our gang, huh?"
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[1]Akane: "What...!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ajiri_reverse]\AA[2]Yui: "Don't play dumb! You know, right? How to tell apart us
gal bitches from the rest!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sion_reverse]\AA[2]Shion: "If not, you couldn't do something like this...!! Who
are you going to pick up next? Gyahaha...! I won't let
you... do it!!"
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Amma: "You're looking for Mei, aren't you?"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[1]Akane: "!!"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Amma: "I knew it!! Haha!! You can't lie...!! It's so
obvious! Akane Suzaku!!"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[1]Akane: "(Damn it!... She saw right through me...!!)"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Amma: "Plus, you were trying to go downstairs, weren't you!!
Not towards the classrooms!! Aahh~ I see now~!!"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Amma: "Mei's location is... in the library after all, huh~?"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[1]Akane: "Gah!!"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Amma: "Gyahahaha...! I was just bluffing, but I hit the
bullseye, didn't I? You really aren't cut out for this kind
of thing!!"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[1]Akane: "(Is it my fault...!?)"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Amma: "Hey! You guys hold her off!! I'm going to pick up
Mei~♪"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ajiri_reverse]\AA[2]Yui: "Akane~♪ Let's lick those flashy dicks together and
smoke some cigarettes~♪ Smoky dicks taste so good when
they're mixed with dick cheese♪"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sion_reverse]\AA[2]Shion: "Gyahahaha! I'll teach you thoroughly!! So that even
a stuck-up bitch like you can become a proper gal!!"

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "Damn it!! To think that the teachers would get in
the way!"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ajiri_reverse]\AA[2]Yui: "It's the master's orders! We don't care what you
think!"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sion_reverse]\AA[2]Shion: "I'll teach you about the harshness of society! The
strong ones win, that's how it is!!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sion_reverse]\AA[1]Akane: "Even if I have to take a detour... I'll rescue
her!!"
A
